description: With the Arlen Bystander skill, Alexa knows all thirteen seasons of the television series King of the Hill. Ask for an episode from a particular season, and Alexa will pick one at random. The episode title, number, and description are provided.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask the Arlen Bystander to give me an episode from season one.
What's an episode from season three?
Find me an episode from season thirteen.
name: The Arlen Bystander
shortDescription: Ask the Arlen Bystander for random episodes of the television show King of the Hill.
